---
title: Chicken Cotoletta Suprema Subs with Prosciutto, Fresh Mozzarella & Balsamic Dressed Arugula
description: Crispy fried chicken cutlets get the star treatment in these loaded Italian-style subs. Layer those juicy cutlets onto toasted baguettes, then pile with salty prosciutto, fresh mozzarella, and juicy tomato slices, and serve with a fresh, peppery arugula salad tossed in tangy balsamic vinaigrette.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d70e6007a263836a73e9c7-dcd2b7d8.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66d70e6007a263836a73e9c7-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 25 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: Southern Europe
nutrition:
  calories: 910 kcal
  fat: 41 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 59 g
  sugar: 16 g
  protein: 55 g
